### API test pakai REST Client VS Code Extension
### Harus sudah jalan server di localhost:8080
### Klik "Send Request" di atas setiap request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

#categories

### GET All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories

### GET Category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1

### POST Create Category - Makanan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Makanan",
    "description": "Kategori makanan dan nasi"
}

