### TRANSACTION / CHECKOUT

### POST Checkout - Single Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "items": [
        {
            "product_id": 1,
            "quantity": 2
        }
    ]
}

### POST Checkout - Multiple Items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "items": [
        {
            "product_id": 1,
            "quantity": 2
        },
        {
            "product_id": 2,
            "quantity": 1
        },
        {
            "product_id": 4,
            "quantity": 3
        }
    ]
}

### POST Checkout - Bulk Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "items": [
        {
            "product_id": 3,
            "quantity": 5
        },
        {
            "product_id": 4,
            "quantity": 10
        }
    ]
}

### SALES REPORT

### GET Daily Sales Report - Today's Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/report/hari-ini

### GET Sales Report - Date Range (Example: Jan 1 to Feb 28, 2026)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/report?start_date=2026-01-01&end_date=2026-02-28

### GET Sales Report - Last 7 Days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/report?start_date=2026-01-31&end_date=2026-02-07

### GET Sales Report - Custom Range (Jan 15 to Jan 31)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/report?start_date=2026-01-15&end_date=2026-01-31


### ERROR HANDLING TEST

### Test Invalid Category ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/9999

### Test Invalid Product ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/produk/9999

### Test Invalid Date Format
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/report?start_date=01-01-2026&end_date=28-02-2026

### Test Missing Required Fields - Invalid Checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "items": []
}
### NOTES:
### - Product prices dalam IDR (Rupiah)
### - Stock akan otomatis berkurang saat checkout
### - Report menampilkan total_revenue, total_transaksi, dan produk_terlaris
### - Semua response dalam format JSO
